N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14 ยง 343.10 - Reporting

State Regulations
(a) Required
reports. Certified providers must prepare and provide the division with
statistical, financial, pre and post test format and/or results, and evaluative
reports at such times as requested and on forms provided by the
division. (b) Failure to report. Failure to submit such reports may result in termination of certification in
accordance with section
343.15
of this Part or denial of
renewal of certification in accordance with section
343.14
of this Part. Notes
